product.title: Igloo Cup Vanilla
product.description: Ice cream is a frozen dairy dessert obtained by freezing the ice cream mix with continuous agitation. It contains milk products, sweetening materials, stabilizers, colors, flavors, and egg products. Ice cream had its origins in Europe and was introduced later in the United States where it developed into an industry.
